  <!-- WHAT IS VALUE DYNAMICS? -->
  <section id="what-is">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>What Is Value Dynamics?</h2>
      <p>
        Value Dynamics is the study of how value (both tangible and intangible) flows bidirectionally among players/participants (constituents) in a bounded ecosystem (aka value network).
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Value Network:</strong> The ecosystem where all related actors (customers, partners, suppliers) interact.</li>
        <li><strong>Constituents:</strong> The diverse players making up your network.</li>
        <li><strong>Value Exchange:</strong> The two-way flow of different forms of value—money, products, data, or even trust.</li>
        <li><strong>Value Currencies:</strong> The various forms of value traded, such as money, services, data, and time savings.</li>
        <li><strong>API:</strong> The digital bridges enabling seamless value exchange in modern ecosystems.</li>
        <li><strong>The Value Dynamics Mapping canvas:</strong> A simple, lightweight, yet powerful tool designed to help you visualize, understand, and analyze how value flows within your business ecosystem/organization.</li>
      </ul>
      <!-- Large placeholder image for a future JPEG file -->
      <img src="https://i.imghippo.com/files/YvE5221gs.jpg" alt="Large Placeholder Image" class="placeholder-image">
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BASIC USE CASES -->
  <section id="use-cases">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>What Can It Be Used For?</h2>
      <p>Explore these essential use cases:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Analyze Existing Business Models:</strong> Map your current network to identify imbalances or value “leakage.”</li>
        <li><strong>Define New Business Models:</strong> Sketch “what-if” scenarios to reinvent your business or explore adjacent markets.</li>
        <li><strong>Find New Value Channels:</strong> Find fresh routes—APIs, digital platforms, alliances—to reach customers effectively.</li>
        <li><strong>Augment Current Value Exchanges:</strong> Optimize key interactions like supplier contracts or customer onboarding to extract more value.</li>
        <li><strong>Optimize Supply-Side Exchanges:</strong> Diversify or deepen partnerships to balance cost, quality, and resilience.</li>
        <li><strong>Connect Value Networks:</strong> Bridge your ecosystem with complementary networks for cross-pollination of value.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

